description: Katie, Ashley, and Jay, commonly known as The KAJ, celebrate their 100th episode by doing what they do best, famously: talking about Tom Brady (21:05), The XFL and the Bang Bang Fang Gang (42:42), The Knicks (1:03:23), some weird MLB Reality TV rules (1:06:44), Siba the Poodle (1:15:23), and the USWNT and their CBA (1:18:14). Later, there is, of course, a Bachelor Update (1:35:24) and Erotic News (1:34:19). They end with a voifmail from Aaron (1:42:32). Fwa fwa fwa fwaaaa.
